# [[four]]

====Etymology====
The original shell and bone character was [[一]] written four times (compare [[二]] and [[三]]). The bronzware style of the character featured a repositioning of those four lines inside [[口]]; this later evolved into the combination used today of 口 ''[[mouth]]'' and 八 ''[[divide]]'' which meant ''a dispersal of breath''. It could thus be said that [[four]] is a borrowed meaning for this character.

